    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到 Polity！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/ee55ca98d127b6686422b42f037210ed.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/ee55ca98d127b6686422b42f037210ed.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/ee55ca98d127b6686422b42f037210ed.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>跳上悬浮艇，前往蓝点 2！这颗星球由 Snotra 发现，Snotra 是由地球上的善意智慧创造的超先进人工智能，这颗星球闪耀着希望！Snotra 负责殖民新世界，将人类的智慧和价值观传播到宇宙各地，她创造了人类和机器人来居住这颗星球，并监督了一个反映地球自身的社会的诞生。<br><br>Snotra 指导她的人民几个世纪后，现在已经退后一步，让他们独立繁荣。人类和机器人一起继续朝着她曾经设想的完美乌托邦努力。你会加入他们吗，伸出援手，一起铸造更光明的未来，同时在这颗星球上开辟你自己的位置吗？蓝点 2 正在等待你！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >展示你的风格</h2><br>自定义你的模拟角色，并创造你想象中的完美头像。释放你内在的时尚设计师，选择海量的衣服和配饰。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/5716624af2743353b884e761d9919154.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/5716624af2743353b884e761d9919154.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/5716624af2743353b884e761d9919154.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握新技能</h2><br>学习各种技能，并在你个人的专业工作坊中练习你的手艺。通过深入的制作系统前进，生产有价值的产品，并建立一个贸易帝国。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/788d54c0082c61f5b27a9360f3a4e8cf.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/788d54c0082c61f5b27a9360f3a4e8cf.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/788d54c0082c61f5b27a9360f3a4e8cf.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩拼图和迷你游戏</h2><br>接受任务，并通过玩数十种独特的拼图和迷你游戏来赚取奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/1183f1f00ae3fde2722f8cc164d91e2b.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/1183f1f00ae3fde2722f8cc164d91e2b.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/1183f1f00ae3fde2722f8cc164d91e2b.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在镇上变得流行</h2><br>与其他玩家聊天，以多种方式表达自己，如动画、表情符号、聊天气球和个人资料图片。结交新朋友，并创建自己的聊天组。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/601acd630900476ec569abbb73b06586.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/601acd630900476ec569abbb73b06586.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/601acd630900476ec569abbb73b06586.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索世界</h2><br>探索充满数千个独特岛屿和数百个 NPC 的广阔星球 BD2。跟随为期一年的故事，每月解锁新的地点，并寻找世界最大的谜团的答案。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/f625b22aad588431ec31d58cde8db873.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/f625b22aad588431ec31d58cde8db873.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/f625b22aad588431ec31d58cde8db873.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装饰你的地方</h2><br>用丰富的家具选择装饰你的房子、商店或工作坊。你可以同时拥有多个地方，以最大限度地释放你的创造力。你甚至可以建立自己的殖民地，并按照你的意愿设计所有城市和建筑！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/adafa7c82a4b7de9b59db70df2012fb0.poster.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/adafa7c82a4b7de9b59db70df2012fb0.webm?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/adafa7c82a4b7de9b59db70df2012fb0.mp4?t=1724830804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>BD2 见！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479480/extras/f92e79e13e3d8d0c22ccb8ea2267dd1c.avif?t=1724830804\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
